    "apply_url": "https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/replit/51f1babc-8d3a-4f4a-9def-5b55bba57c8e/application",
    "company": "Replit",
    "compensation": "",
    "content_hash": "a62f473880464057",
    "department": "GTM",
    "description": "Replit is the agentic software creation platform that enables anyone to build applications using natural language. With millions of users worldwide, Replit is democratizing software development by removing traditional barriers to application creation.\n\n\n\nABOUT VIBECON\n\nVibeCon is a cultural AI event at the intersection of technology, art, music, fashion, and creativity. It’s not a traditional tech conference, it’s a high-taste, culture-first experience designed for builders and creatives shaping the future.\n\nvibecon.ai http://vibecon.ai\n\n\nROLE OVERVIEW\n\nWe’re looking for a Social Content Creator to own and execute VibeCon’s social presence from now through the event in June. Your mission: make VibeCon feel culturally unavoidable and sell out the event through content.\n\nYou’ll operate as a highly autonomous, taste-driven creator, someone who can both set the creative direction and execute daily.\n\n\nWHAT YOU’LL DO\n\n - Concept, shoot, edit, and publish content across social platforms\n\n - Create a consistent stream of short-form, high-impact content\n\n - Develop original ideas with strong hooks and clear perspective\n\n - Create moments that generate urgency and social proof\n\n - Collaborate with creators, communities, and pages to amplify reach\n\n\n\nHOW YOU’LL WORK\n\n - Operate as a solo owner of content (while directing collaborators when needed)\n\n - Prioritize speed, taste, and consistency\n\n - Think like both a creator and a creative director\n\n\n\nWHAT WE’RE LOOKING FOR\n\n - Strong instincts for internet culture and storytelling\n\n - Ability to create high-quality, high-volume content quickly\n\n - Clear sense of taste and creative judgment\n\n - Experience building momentum for events, brands, or cultural projects\n\nFull-Time Employee Benefits Include:\n\n💰 Competitive Salary \u0026 Equity\n\n💹 401(k) Program with a 4% match\n\n⚕️ Health, Dental, Vision and Life Insurance\n\n🩼 Short Term and Long Term Disability\n\n🚼 Paid Parental, Medical, Caregiver Leave\n\n🚗 Commuter Benefits\n\n📱 Monthly Wellness Stipend\n\n🧑‍💻 Autonomous Work Environment\n\n🖥 In Office Set-Up Reimbursement\n\n🏝 Flexible Time Off (FTO) + Holidays\n\n🚀 Quarterly Team Gatherings\n\n☕ In Office Amenities\n\nWant to learn more about what we are up to?\n\n - Meet the Replit Agent https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IYiVPrxY8-Y\n\n - Replit: Make an app for that https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4zd9hzngFwY\n\n - Replit Blog https://blog.replit.com/\n\n - Amjad TED Talk https://youtu.be/kCudFI4tcpg?si=l4ViCejV_f2RZkDi\n\nInterviewing + Culture at Replit\n\n - Operating Principles https://blog.replit.com/operating-principles\n\n - Reasons not to work at Replit https://blog.replit.com/reasons-not-to-join-replit\n\nTo achieve our mission of making programming more accessible around the world, we need our team to be representative of the world. We welcome your unique perspective and experiences in shaping this product. We encourage people from all kinds of backgrounds to apply, including and especially candidates from underrepresented and non-traditional backgrounds.",
